HEADWORD: Hyosternal
<hw>Hy`o*ster"nal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Hyo-</ets>
+ <ets>ternal</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>Between
